snippet.textDisplay: Always been a big fan of arnob,his songs changed my life, i sang tomar jonno numerous times like million other bangladeshis in many occasions including my sisters wedding prg. Brishti raat a is one of my most favorites. But this song id like to simply appreciate the ranges of Sunidhi"s voice and classic/raga/fusion/jazz, if india has her of her own,we also claim her as ours hehe. Unbelievable song and composition,this will be really tough to cover for any artist. Worth listenting to again and again during drives on rainy days and nights and also at home, when you want to feel real music and not our synthesizer singers.
